&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;New York preferred | Remote&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Talent Wanted. For hazardous journey. &lt;s&gt;Small wages&lt;/s&gt;, bitter cold, long months of complete darkness, constant danger, safe return doubtful. Honour and recognition in case of success.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fridtjof Nansen crossed the Arctic, going places no human had ever been. Together with our users, we’re doing the same onchain: charting entirely new territory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nansen is a special company. We&#39;re building the single best product for onchain investing, allowing &lt;em&gt;A New Way To Trade&lt;/em&gt; that’s agentic, onchain, and fully integrated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re looking for an adventure, you’ve come to the right place.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our mission:&lt;/strong&gt; Surface the signal and create winners&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What you&#39;ll do at Nansen&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You own the full sales cycle in the staking vertical. Foundations, ecosystem teams, institutional holders — these are your prospects. From first outreach to signed contract, from renewal to expansion, this is your book.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the complete sales cycle: prospect, qualify, close, renew, and expand partnerships with blockchain foundations and ecosystem teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the end-to-end launch of new validator ecosystems: initial scoping, commercial negotiation, delegation activation, and go-to-market execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and engage institutional holders and ecosystem leads who need staking infrastructure and validator partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track new chain launches, protocol developments, and market shifts to find opportunities before they&#39;re obvious&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with product, marketing, and customer success to close complex deals and retain accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What we&#39;re looking for&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–5 years in sales or business development, with a track record that shows up in numbers: quota attainment, deal size, account growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge of the crypto ecosystem: who the key players are, how capital moves, which protocols matter. You know who actually moves volume&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ year of staking-specific BD or sales experience. Validators, liquid staking protocols, institutional staking infrastructure — you understand how this market works&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working cross-functionally with product, marketing, and customer success to navigate complex deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You use AI to move faster: prospecting research, call prep, deal intelligence. Show us what that looks like in practice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Candidates must already have the legal right to work in the US at the time of application&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice-to-have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based in New York, with the ability to travel for partner meetings and events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An existing network across validator operators, L1/L2 foundations, or institutional staking teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What we offer our crew&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary. Meaningful equity. Real ownership in what you build&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fully remote with two no-meeting days a week — because deep work doesn&#39;t happen in a Google Meet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Annual company retreat and team off-sites in one of our offices: Singapore, Bangkok, London, and Oslo — flights and accommodation covered&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unlimited AI tokens — Claude, OpenAI, whatever helps you move fast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your own OpenClaw for work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nansen Pro account — full access to the most detailed onchain data in the market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team of 80+ builders that started as data engineers and scientists. The people who built the product you&#39;re sellin

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Blockchain Compliance Analyst&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Bhutan | Full-time&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nansen is a leading AI-powered blockchain intelligence platform, trusted by crypto traders, investors, and builders worldwide. We&#39;ve gone from being the leader in onchain analytics to the leader in agentic trading — and our compliance program needs to keep pace.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our mission:&lt;/strong&gt; Surface the signal and create winners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What you&#39;ll do at Nansen&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Compliance at Nansen isn&#39;t about checklists. It&#39;s about understanding how money moves onchain — and catching what doesn&#39;t add up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct blockchain forensics: trace fund flows, identify risk patterns, and assess exposure to designated risk categories across chains&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As part of our AML/CFT program, run transaction monitoring for clients: investigate alerts from on-chain monitoring systems, perform end-to-end case investigations — gather data, review KYC/customer profiles, analyze counterparties and wallets, document rationale, and recommend closure or escalation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, monitor, and maintain the compliance automations that keep these programs running at scale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write clear, structured reports that communicate findings to internal and external stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to internal training by sharing typologies, red flags, and case learnings — and help drive continuous improvement in monitoring quality and efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on regulatory developments, enforcement actions, and financial crime trends affecting crypto/onchain businesses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What we&#39;re looking for&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Genuine curiosity about how blockchains work — not just conceptually, but mechanically&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical mindset: able to identify patterns, connect disparate data points, and ask the right questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail combined with the ability to see the bigger picture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written communication: you can make complex findings readable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Takes ownership and runs without waiting to be asked&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Nice to have&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with blockchain analytics tools and explorers (e.g. Nansen, Etherscan, Chainalysis, Elliptic)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with AML frameworks or financial crime compliance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SQL or Python skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior exposure to DeFi protocols, wallets, or exchange flows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;New graduates welcome&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You don&#39;t need years of experience. A degree in artificial intelligence, blockchain, cybersecurity, finance, accounting, economics, business, or a related field is a plus — but what matters more is that you&#39;re sharp, curious, and want to learn fast from inside a crypto-native AI company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What we offer our crew&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary. Meaningful equity. Real ownership in what you build.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Annual company retreat and team off-sites in one of our offices: Singapore, Bangkok, London, and Oslo — flights and accommodation covered&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unlimited AI tokens — Claude, OpenAI, whatever helps you move fast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your own OpenClaw for work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nansen Pro account — full access to the most detailed onchain data in the market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team that started as data engineers and data scientists, now 80+ builders. Your craft is respected here.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Speed, ownership, curiosity, courage. These aren&#39;t values on a wall — they&#39;re how we run.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A front-row seat — and a hand in building — the next chapter of finance&lt;/li&gt;
&

&lt;p&gt;Nansen surfaces the signal and creates winners in the future of finance. We&#39;re building a new way to trade: agentic, onchain, and fully integrated. From analytics to execution, we&#39;re the platform where investors find alpha and act on it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re building a world-class support team in Bhutan to be closer to our users around the clock. This is an early and important hire — you&#39;ll be among the first on the ground, working directly with our global CS and product teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Customer Support Agent, you&#39;ll be the human behind the help. You&#39;ll work alongside our AI support agent (Thor) to resolve user issues, escalate where needed, and make sure every Nansen user feels genuinely taken care of.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This isn&#39;t a ticket-grinding job. We&#39;re building a lean, AI-augmented support function — that means you&#39;ll handle the cases that need real judgment, empathy, and creative problem-solving, while Thor handles the repetitive front line.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to user support requests across Zendesk and Discord community channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Triage, investigate, and resolve issues related to account access, billing, data discrepancies, and product usage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate complex technical or product issues to the appropriate internal teams with clear documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work alongside Thor (our AI support agent) — reviewing AI-generated responses, catching errors, and improving its outputs over time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collect and surface user feedback to the product team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help build and maintain our support knowledge base (FAQs, help docs, canned responses)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in onboarding sessions and ongoing training as the product evolves&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Must-haves:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written English — clear, concise, and empathetic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–5 years of customer support, customer success, or service experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working with digital tools and picking up new software quickly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Patient, detail-oriented, and calm under pressure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Genuinely curious about crypto and blockchain — you don&#39;t need to be an expert, but you need to want to become one&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior exposure to crypto, DeFi, or fintech products (even as a user)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a tech startup or fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with support tools (Zendesk, Intercom, or similar)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with AI-assisted tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;445&quot; data-end=&quot;471&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;445&quot; data-end=&quot;471&quot;&gt;Additional Information:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;If your application is successful and you progress to the offer stage, you will be required to complete two professional reference checks and a basic background screening as part of our hiring process.&lt;/p&gt;

